window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Divorce. Divide. </p> <p>Gage Falcon's life is turned upside down. When backed against a wall, he does what men with \"steel\" convictions do...take control. </p> <p>Fight. Strength. </p> <p>Phoenix Star knows it's going to take everything inside her to be who she is destined to be. Fresh out of college and knowing she can't go home and get where she wants to get, she takes the path less traveled. Redefining life sends them both down a long dirt road to...become. </p> <p>What happens when two people starting over in life and needing to find some control come face to face? </p> <p>They get...hammered! </p> <p>Contains mature themes. </p>"; 
